<plot>Julio, a young Mixtec, returns to Los Trios, his birthplace. There he tasked by his dying mother with protecting his father's grave from a government sponsored road that is being built through the graveyard he lies in. Julio reluctantly agrees and is then left alone in this new world. He struggles to understand the value of saving the grave and indeed the values his mother and father.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?306560</url></doc>
